PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of CLÉMENT GAUDREAU, of Montmagny, Quebec, as a part-time director of the board of directors of the Port of Quebec Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of ten months, in the place of William Keays, whose term has expired.
Attachments
precis:
Approval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of
CLÉMENT GAUDREAU, of Montmagny, Quebec, as a part-time director of the
board of directors of the Port of Quebec Corporation to hold office
during pleasure for a term of ten months, in the place of William Keays,
whose term has expired.
